<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>비회원 주문조회 | DAMORE</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --bg: #f5f3ef;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --black: #111111;
      --muted: #6f6a63;
      --line: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.08);
      --gold: #9d8660;
      --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      --radius: 24px;
      --max: 860px;
      --soft: #efe9df;
      --red: #b23a2c;
      --red-bg: #fff1ee;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--black);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }

    button,
    input {
      font: inherit;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: var(--max);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px;
    }

    .page {
      padding: 44px 0 80px;
    }

    .page-head {
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .page-head small {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .page-head h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .page-head p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .top-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .top-btn {
      min-width: 160px;
      height: 48px;
      padding: 0 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      border: 0;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .top-btn-dark {
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .top-btn-light {
      background: var(--soft);
      color: #111;
    }

    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .section-desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    input[type="text"],
    input[type="tel"] {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      outline: none;
      background: #fff;
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    input[type="text"]:focus,
    input[type="tel"]:focus {
      border-color: rgba(157, 134, 96, 0.8);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(157, 134, 96, 0.12);
    }

    .input-help {
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .error-box {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: var(--red-bg);
      color: var(--red);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .error-text {
      display: block;
      min-height: 18px;
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--red);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .submit-btn {
      width: 100%;
      height: 56px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .note-box {
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #faf8f4;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .container {
        padding: 0 16px;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .page-head h1 {
        font-size: 34px;
      }

      .top-btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-head">
        <small>Guest Order Lookup</small>
        <h1>비회원 주문조회</h1>
        <p>주문번호와 연락처를 입력하면 비회원 주문내역을 확인할 수 있습니다.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="top-actions">
        <a href="/" class="top-btn top-btn-dark">상품 목록 가기</a>
        <a href="/my-orders" class="top-btn top-btn-light">회원 주문내역 보기</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="section-title">주문 조회 정보 입력</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">주문 시 입력한 연락처와 정확한 주문번호를 입력해주세요.</p>

        <% if (error) { %>
          <div class="error-box"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>

        <form method="POST" action="/order/lookup" id="lookupForm">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="orderId">주문번호</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="orderId"
              name="orderId"
              value="<%= orderId || '' %>"
              placeholder="주문번호를 입력해주세요"
            />
            <small class="error-text" id="orderIdError"></small>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="phone">연락처</label>
            <input
              type="tel"
              id="phone"
              name="phone"
              value="<%= phone || '' %>"
              placeholder="010-0000-0000"
              maxlength="13"
            />
            <div class="input-help">숫자만 입력해도 자동으로 하이픈이 들어갑니다.</div>
            <small class="error-text" id="phoneError"></small>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">주문 조회하기</button>
        </form>

        <div class="note-box">
          비회원 주문조회는 주문번호와 연락처가 모두 일치해야 확인할 수 있습니다.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script>
    const form = document.getElementById('lookupForm');
    const orderIdInput = document.getElementById('orderId');
    const phoneInput = document.getElementById('phone');
    const orderIdError = document.getElementById('orderIdError');
    const phoneError = document.getElementById('phoneError');

    function formatPhone(value) {
      const numbers = value.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '').slice(0, 11);

      if (numbers.length < 4) return numbers;
      if (numbers.length < 8) return numbers.slice(0, 3) + '-' + numbers.slice(3);
      return numbers.slice(0, 3) + '-' + numbers.slice(3, 7) + '-' + numbers.slice(7);
    }

    function clearErrors() {
      orderIdError.textContent = '';
      phoneError.textContent = '';
    }

    function validateForm(orderId, phone) {
      let valid = true;
      clearErrors();

      if (!orderId) {
        orderIdError.textContent = '주문번호를 입력해주세요.';
        valid = false;
      }

      if (!phone) {
        phoneError.textContent = '연락처를 입력해주세요.';
        valid = false;
      } else {
        const onlyNumbers = phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '');
        if (onlyNumbers.length < 10 || onlyNumbers.length > 11) {
          phoneError.textContent = '연락처 형식을 다시 확인해주세요.';
          valid = false;
        }
      }

      return valid;
    }

    phoneInput.addEventListener('input', function () {
      phoneInput.value = formatPhone(phoneInput.value);
    });

    form.addEventListener('submit', function (e) {
      const orderId = orderIdInput.value.trim();
      const phone = phoneInput.value.trim();

      if (!validateForm(orderId, phone)) {
        e.preventDefault();
      }
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>